<div class="bb-intro">
    <h1>Hello, Brouter!</h1>
    <p class="bb-subtitle">A tour of <code>Bit.Brouter</code> routing features. Pick any link below to see it in action.</p>
</div>

<div class="bb-counter">
    <div>
        <div class="bb-counter-label">Current count</div>
        <div class="bb-counter-value">@CountValue</div>
    </div>
    <div style="color: var(--bb-text-muted); font-size: .85rem;">
        The shared count is preserved across navigations via the host component.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="bb-grid">
    <section class="bb-card">
        <h3 class="bb-card-title">
            <span class="bb-dot bb-dot-primary"></span>
            Route parameters
            <span class="bb-badge">params</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="bb-card-desc">Strongly-typed route values with optional and multi-segment constraints.</p>
        <ul class="bb-link-list">
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/counter/1234">Counter starting at <code>1234</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/counter/multi/1/2/saleh">Multi-param: <code>/multi/1/2/saleh</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/profile">Profile (no username)</BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/profile/saleh">Profile of <code>saleh</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/posts/2026/05/intro-to-brouter">Catch-all post slug</BrouterLink></li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bb-card">
        <h3 class="bb-card-title">
            <span class="bb-dot bb-dot-warning"></span>
            Wildcards &amp; fallbacks
            <span class="bb-badge bb-badge-warn">wildcard</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="bb-card-desc">How wildcard segments and the 404 fallback resolve.</p>
        <ul class="bb-link-list">
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/hahahaha/test">Wildcard <code>*/test</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/start/test2/end">Pattern <code>{prefix}/test2/{postfix}</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/404-test">Non-existent page</BrouterLink></li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bb-card">
        <h3 class="bb-card-title">
            <span class="bb-dot bb-dot-success"></span>
            Nested routes
            <span class="bb-badge bb-badge-success">nested</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="bb-card-desc">Routes with their own children and outlets.</p>
        <ul class="bb-link-list">
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/nested-route/1">Nested example <code>/1</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/nested-route/5/hello">Nested example <code>/5/hello</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/nested-route/10/world">Nested example <code>/10/world</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/nested-route/22/404-test">Non-existent nested route</BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/nested">Nested layout</BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/nested2">Nested2 layout</BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/nested3">Nested3 layout</BrouterLink></li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bb-card">
        <h3 class="bb-card-title">
            <span class="bb-dot bb-dot-danger"></span>
            Guarded routes
            <span class="bb-badge bb-badge-danger">guard</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="bb-card-desc">Routes that conditionally redirect via guards, cancel leaves, or block outright.</p>
        <ul class="bb-link-list">
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/g1">/g1 - allowed when <code>second % 2 == 0</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/g2">/g2 - allowed when <code>minute % 2 == 0</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/editor">Leave guard - unsaved-changes editor</BrouterLink></li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bb-card">
        <h3 class="bb-card-title">
            <span class="bb-dot bb-dot-primary"></span>
            Data layer
            <span class="bb-badge">loader</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="bb-card-desc">
            Loaders, the <code>StaleTime</code> cache, revalidation, deferred data and error boundaries.
            The links below <strong>preload on hover</strong> (<code>Preload="Intent"</code>) - rest the
            pointer on one for a moment and the slow loader is already done when you click.
        </p>
        <ul class="bb-link-list">
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/data" Preload="BrouterLinkPreload.Intent">Loader + cache + revalidate + query updates</BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/deferred" Preload="BrouterLinkPreload.Intent">Deferred (streamed) data via <code>BrouterAwait</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/unstable">Error boundary with retry (loader throws)</BrouterLink></li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bb-card">
        <h3 class="bb-card-title">
            <span class="bb-dot bb-dot-warning"></span>
            Navigation control
            <span class="bb-badge bb-badge-warn">nav</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="bb-card-desc">Awaited outcomes, history entry state, and the .NET 10 NotFound interop.</p>
        <ul class="bb-link-list">
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/outcomes">Awaited navigation (<code>NavigateAsync</code>) + <code>NotFound()</code></BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/history-state">History entry state across Back/Forward</BrouterLink></li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bb-card">
        <h3 class="bb-card-title">
            <span class="bb-dot bb-dot-success"></span>
            Layout &amp; state
            <span class="bb-badge bb-badge-success">layout</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="bb-card-desc">Named outlets, pathless groups, keep-alive routes, and animated page changes via the View Transitions API.</p>
        <ul class="bb-link-list">
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/gallery"><strong>View Transitions gallery</strong> - shared-element morphs between routes</BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/dashboard/stats">Named outlets + pathless group (dashboard)</BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/sticky">Keep-alive route + activate/deactivate lifecycle</BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/fleeting">Transient control route (state resets)</BrouterLink></li>
            <li><BrouterLink Href="/notes/1">Per-parameter keep-alive (<code>KeepAliveMax</code>) + <code>ClearKeepAlive()</code></BrouterLink></li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</div>

@code {
    [Parameter] public int CountValue { get; set; }
}
